*******************************************
RG	gate g		{Rg}
RS	s kat		{Rs}
RM	d s		100k
RC	d dr		{0.1*Rg}
CGS	g s		{Cgs}
COX	g ox		{Cox}
*****************************
* voltage across depletion region below gate:
EDEP	dr ox	VALUE = {Vdep(V(d,g))}
* current through base resistor:
GIA	ano e 	VALUE = {V(ano,e)/Rb(V(b))}
* charge control:
GIQ	e d	VALUE = {IQ(V(d,kat),I(VDXJ),I(VINE),V(b))}
* collector (hole) current:
